  <span id="freeText12091749298214922966" style="display:none">Dreaming My Animal Selves by Helene Cardona is a meandering , meditative journey into the very essence of nature. Refreshing and rejuvenating the soul with her gently flowing words and dreams the final lines in her poem Pathway to Gifts epitomizes this feeling " The dream opens forgotten realms of creation. I think that's what time is." A book certainly to treasure.</span>
