              <span id="reviewTextContainer1059603955" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17289624693354116657">Read this lovely work twice, including the French verses (that escape the membrance of my four years of studied language), imagining Helene&apos;s distinguished accented words, summoning me to translate in her voice, the importance and significance of dreams, animals, this life. A delightful, mystical journey into the imagination!<br/><br/>&quot;...I reach the gate<br/>between my past and the waterway.<br/>Like the penguin, I lay on a leaf,<br/>let the river transport me<br/>knowing I&apos;ve entered another world.&quot;<br/><br/> Helene Cardona</span>
