    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer621929033" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8068651653800697559">Helene Cardona takes her poetry to a new level of class and quality in this latest book.<br/>Dreaming My Animal Selves is a work both mystical and magical in the way it stirs the mind as well as the spirit.<br/>The depth of thoughts, the delight of the images and the expert use of language all show growth as an artist and come as a wonderful reward for the reader.<br/>She writes in English and French but this collection is magnifique in any language</span>

          </span>
        </div>


