              <span id="reviewTextContainer662374318" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18038530620733201940">The further you delve into this book the deeper down the rabbit hole you will go. <br/><br/>Beautifully written poetry with a twist of creativity and imagination. <br/><br/>Words become alive and jump of the pages as the author dreams her animal selves. <br/><br/>Some of my favorite poems include:Isle of the Immortals, Breeze Rider,Dreamer, A Mind like the Sky, and Transparencies of Thought<br/><br/>This book is written in both French and English. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


