<div id="review_669010312" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/669010312" />
    <a title="Tristan" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5368996-tristan"><img alt="Tristan" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/669010312?book_show_action=true">Jul 16, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Tristan" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Tristan" href="/user/show/5368996-tristan">Tristan</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer669010312" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2208617553642672950">I am absolutely in love with this Gem of a book! There is so much power contained within its pages. It is a gorgeous poetic odyssey. The book is as captivating and layered as Hélène Cardona herself. Her gifted verse, awakens the Dream Self and takes the reader on an enriching journey of self discovery. Her words are a wise friend, encouraging deep reflection. Wondrous and unforgettable, &quot;Dreaming My Animal Selves&quot; is a work of art that is among the best of 2013! </span>
  <span id="freeText2208617553642672950" style="display:none">I am absolutely in love with this Gem of a book! There is so much power contained within its pages. It is a gorgeous poetic odyssey. The book is as captivating and layered as Hélène Cardona herself. Her gifted verse, awakens the Dream Self and takes the reader on an enriching journey of self discovery. Her words are a wise friend, encouraging deep reflection. Wondrous and unforgettable, "Dreaming My Animal Selves" is a work of art that is among the best of 2013! </span>
