      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer601314882" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14029072504289995678">Helene Cardona’s delightful new book of poetry published by Salmon Poetry and titled, “Dreaming My Animal Selves / Le Songe de mes Âmes Animales” is a richly woven tapestry of metaphor and sensate imagery. Discover your own “Animal Selves” within these pages of indelible poems by Ms. Cardona.<br/><br/>R Jeffreys<br/>Associate Editor<br/>The Tiferet Journal <br/></span>

