<div id="review_652864681" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/652864681" />
    <a title="Josephine Wallace" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/21712629-josephine-wallace"><img alt="Josephine Wallace" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/652864681?book_show_action=true">Jun 27, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Josephine Wallace" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Josephine Wallace" href="/user/show/21712629-josephine-wallace">Josephine Wallace</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer652864681" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17342784902946274096">Cardona invites her readers to a luscious, deeply felt world. The poems, in French and English, have a clean and elegant style that doesn&apos;t upstage the powerful archetypes that Cardona brings to life. This is a book that will charm all readers, even those who resist poetry, and it makes a wonderful gift. I highly recommend this volume, and look forward to more work from the author.</span>
  <span id="freeText17342784902946274096" style="display:none">Cardona invites her readers to a luscious, deeply felt world. The poems, in French and English, have a clean and elegant style that doesn't upstage the powerful archetypes that Cardona brings to life. This is a book that will charm all readers, even those who resist poetry, and it makes a wonderful gift. I highly recommend this volume, and look forward to more work from the author.</span>
