  <span id="freeText7959360777909839604" style="display:none">In Helene Cardona's "Dreaming My Animal Selves/Le Songe de mes Ames Animales" we travel through an infinite space of imagination guided by an intelligent, multicultural poet. This surreal journey propels through myth and fantasy with beautifully crafted and evocative words that cast a luminous aura to this intriguing poetry book.</span>
